    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Technique of emphasizing shadows, darkness or night effects within a painting; generally the use of such shadowing obscures figures within the painting.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
